{"analytics_identifier":"OT1180","base_path":"/government/organisations/national-data-guardian","content_id":"c9fa14af-052d-451c-a003-5d03a13b92b2","description":"The National Data Guardian advises on the use of confidential health and care data, supporting its safe, ethical, and trustworthy use for individual care and public benefit. NDG works with the Department of Health and Social Care .","details":{"acronym":"NDG","alternative_format_contact_email":"","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The National Data Guardian advises on the use of confidential health and care data, supporting its safe, ethical, and trustworthy use for individual care and public benefit.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"National Data Guardian\">NDG</abbr> works with the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/department-of-health-and-social-care\">Department of Health and Social Care</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"department-of-health","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"custom","formatted_title":"National Data<br/>Guardian","image":{"alt_text":"National Data Guardian","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/63244b48d3bf7f1bff8894ef/NDG_logo_cropped.png"}},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/national-data-guardian/about/complaints-procedure","title":"Complaints procedure"},{"href":"/government/organisations/national-data-guardian/about/terms-of-reference","title":"Terms of reference"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Corporate report","href":"/government/publications/national-data-guardian-2024-2025-report","image":{"alt_text":"Dr Nicola Byrne, National Data Guardian","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6942a9c79273c48f554cf50a/s712_NBGOVUK.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6942a9c7fdbd8404f9e1f227/s465_NBGOVUK.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6942a9c736f089d38be1f21d/NBGOVUK.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-12-17T13:01:20.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>This report covers the work of the NDG and her team in 2024–25, including relevant updates outside the period, and outlines priority work through to March 2027.</p>\n</div>","title":"National Data Guardian 2024-2025 report"},{"document_type":"Research","href":"/government/publications/can-communications-create-reasonable-expectations-about-uses-of-health-and-care-data-insights-from-co-design-and-public-testing","image":{"alt_text":"Lightbulb used to indicate a new idea","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6936ad7ba6fc97b81e574348/s712_Lightbulb_ideas_photo_GOV.UK.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6936ad7b7b258b4b52574348/s465_Lightbulb_ideas_photo_GOV.UK.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6936ad7b92da4705a575d3f3/Lightbulb_ideas_photo_GOV.UK.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-12-08T10:41:10.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Findings from a public engagement project testing if co-designed communications can set clear expectations about health and care data use.</p>\n</div>","title":"Can communications create reasonable expectations about uses of health and care data? Insights from co-design and public testing"},{"document_type":"Policy paper","href":"/government/publications/using-data-in-reflective-practice-to-support-safe-care","image":{"alt_text":"Clinician using an electronic device (a tablet)","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6936ae5e92da4705a575d3f6/s712_Doctor_on_device_photo_GOV.UK.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6936ae5e7b258b4b52574349/s465_Doctor_on_device_photo_GOV.UK.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6936ae5eb612700b2cb7360b/Doctor_on_device_photo_GOV.UK.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-12-03T13:53:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>NDG statement on accessing confidential patient information for reflective practice, including safeguards, limits, and links to staff guidance.</p>\n</div>","title":"Using data in reflective practice to support safe care"},{"document_type":"Guidance","href":"/government/publications/what-do-we-mean-by-public-benefit-evaluating-public-benefit-when-health-and-adult-social-care-data-is-used-for-purposes-beyond-individual-care","image":{"alt_text":"Abstract illustration of a crowd of people.","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6399aceae90e072af09c9286/s712_Group_people_abstract_illustration_GOV.UK.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6399acea8fa8f50ddcf03145/s465_Group_people_abstract_illustration_GOV.UK.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6399aceae90e072ae99199f6/Group_people_abstract_illustration_GOV.UK.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2022-12-14T10:56:11.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>This National Data Guardian guidance will improve public benefit evaluations by defining and standardising the concept of public benefit to enable clearer interpretation and understanding.</p>\n</div>","title":"What do we mean by public benefit? Evaluating public benefit when health and adult social care data is used for purposes beyond individual care"},{"document_type":"Guidance","href":"/government/publications/national-data-guardian-guidance-on-the-appointment-of-caldicott-guardians-their-role-and-responsibilities","image":{"alt_text":"Hands on a keyboard","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6398fa4fd3bf7f3f7afd1b54/s712_Hands_on_keyboard_illustration_GOV.UK.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6398fa4fd3bf7f3f87523020/s465_Hands_on_keyboard_illustration_GOV.UK.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6398fa4f8fa8f553028d4f73/Hands_on_keyboard_illustration_GOV.UK.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2021-08-27T07:58:40.000+01:00","